ploads/wm/2024/02/satechi-145-travelcharger-review-10-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"2160\" height=\"1440\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Satechi 145W GaN travel charger with US prongs extended\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/02/satechi-145-travelcharger-review-10-1.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/02/satechi-145-travelcharger-review-10-1.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e Ever since the launch of the iPhone 12 in 2020, most smartphone brands have followed Apple\u0026#39;s lead and stopped including a charger in the box. And more often than not, they nudge you toward buying their own official charger, which usually costs more than alternatives on Amazon or Best Buy. But that\u0026#39;s not the whole truth.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eYou don\u0026#39;t need to use the same brand\u0026#39;s charger for a safe and fast charge. Certified third-party chargers from brands like Anker, Belkin, Spigen, and UGreen meet all necessary safety and charging standards (and cost less than what phone brands might charge you).\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003ePlus, most chargers from these brands support most fast charging protocols, like USB-PD, PPS, and Quick Charge. Unless your device uses very specific proprietary charging tech, like OnePlus\u0026#39; SuperVOOC or Xiaomi\u0026#39;s HyperCharge, chances are a good third-party charger will work just fine.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"wireless-charging-is-totally-safe-and-efficient\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e1 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Wireless charging is totally safe and efficient\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch3 id=\"it-39-s-convenient-but-not-without-trade-offs-in-heat-and-speed\"\u003e\n            It\u0026#39;s convenient, but not without trade-offs in heat and speed\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                        \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/wireless-charging-hero-pixel-stand.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/wireless-charging-hero-pixel-stand.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/wireless-charging-hero-pixel-stand.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/wireless-charging-hero-pixel-stand.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/wireless-charging-hero-pixel-stand.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/wireless-charging-hero-pixel-stand.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/wireless-charging-hero-pixel-stand.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/wireless-charging-hero-pixel-stand.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/wireless-charging-hero-pixel-stand.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Photo of a Pixel 9 Pro on a Pixel Stand wireless charger.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/wireless-charging-hero-pixel-stand.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/wireless-charging-hero-pixel-stand.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e Most Android flagship devices now support wireless charging, and while it\u0026#39;s a convenient feature, it\u0026#39;s not always the best choice for battery health. Wireless charging generates more heat than wired charging. Over time, this heat can cause faster battery degradation, meaning your battery might not hold as much charge as when it was new.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eSo, if possible, avoid using wireless charging regularly. While it\u0026#39;s fine occasionally, if you prefer using a Qi-certified charger regularly, consider wireless chargers that come with built-in fans or temperature regulation, as they help reduce heat generation. That said, wired charging remains one of the best options (and the fact that it\u0026#39;s usually faster helps too).\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n    \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"1aca-4995-84767f776e5e\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t\n\t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/why-wireless-charging-doesnt-make-sense/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/peak-design-qi2-wireless-charger-pixel7a-standing-outdoors.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/peak-design-qi2-wireless-charger-pixel7a-standing-outdoors.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/peak-design-qi2-wireless-charger-pixel7a-standing-outdoors.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/peak-design-qi2-wireless-charger-pixel7a-standing-outdoors.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/peak-design-qi2-wireless-charger-pixel7a-standing-outdoors.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/peak-design-qi2-wireless-charger-pixel7a-standing-outdoors.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/peak-design-qi2-wireless-charger-pixel7a-standing-outdoors.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/peak-design-qi2-wireless-charger-pixel7a-standing-outdoors.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/peak-design-qi2-wireless-charger-pixel7a-standing-outdoors.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"4480\" height=\"2520\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"The Peak Design wireless charging stand with a Pixel 7a outdoors.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/peak-design-qi2-wireless-charger-pixel7a-standing-outdoors.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/peak-design-qi2-wireless-charger-pixel7a-standing-outdoors.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"turns-out-everything-i-knew-about-charging-my-phone-was-wrong\"\u003e\n            Turns out, everything I knew about charging my phone was wrong\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOn the whole, some common misconceptions about charging devices — many dating back to the 2000s — still stick with us. But smartphones have become much smarter over time and can now regulate charging more efficiently through various intelligent features.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eIn fact, beyond knowing these truths, you can \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/save-battery-life-by-changing-these-settings/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eimprove your phone\u0026#39;s battery life\u003c/a\u003e by simply following a few tips and integrating them into your routine.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
